					<p>I agree with puzzlehouse. This is definitely NOT butter chicken. You&#8217;re missing a whole lot of spices and the process is different as well. You should be starting with tandoori chicken and then go from there. </p>
<p>This looks like a delicious dish, but please do not entitle it as Butter Chicken. Then we will start getting a bunch of people making what they think is butter chicken.</p>
